1
00:00:07,042 --> 00:00:09,332
After Xiao Yan subdued the Pure Lotus Demon Flame,

2
00:00:09,333 --> 00:00:11,749
he left the Demon Flame Space with Xun Er.

3
00:00:11,958 --> 00:00:15,999
Concerned for his companions, he rushed back to the Tianfu Alliance.

4
00:00:16,458 --> 00:00:19,791
Meanwhile, the Alliance received a challenge letter for a final battle from the Soul Hall.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:23,374
Yao Lao worried their strength was insufficient to withstand the assault.

6
00:00:23,708 --> 00:00:25,416
But Xiao Yan's return...

7
00:00:25,417 --> 00:00:27,082
not only filled the void in their battle power...

8
00:00:27,083 --> 00:00:30,291
but also ignited everyone's fighting spirit to protect Central Plains.

9
00:00:30,917 --> 00:00:33,707
News of the decisive battle spread throughout Central Plains.

10
00:00:33,708 --> 00:00:36,707
All major powers focused their gaze on the Dipping Fallen Peak.

11
00:00:37,208 --> 00:00:40,124
In this showdown between the Tianfu Alliance and the Soul Hall...

12
00:00:40,167 --> 00:00:44,124
who will become the overlord of Central Plains?

13
00:00:53,042 --> 00:00:54,999
Pray that the Tianfu Alliance wins.

14
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:58,957
So Central Plains no longer has to live under the shadow of the Soul Hall.

15
00:01:00,292 --> 00:01:02,416
You really are alive.

16
00:01:05,083 --> 00:01:06,541
Much obliged for the Hall Master's concern.

17
00:01:06,917 --> 00:01:08,207
Not only did I not die...

18
00:01:08,375 --> 00:01:10,832
but I conveniently refined the Pure Lotus Demon Flame.

19
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:19,666
Never expected that the Xiao Clan could still produce someone comparable to Xiao Xuan.

20
00:01:20,417 --> 00:01:24,207
But the Soul Clan made Xiao Xuan fall...

21
00:01:24,792 --> 00:01:26,041
and as for you...

22
00:01:26,625 --> 00:01:28,291
the result will be the same.

23
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:33,666
This battle today...

24
00:01:34,083 --> 00:01:36,374
if your Tianfu Alliance loses...

25
00:01:36,583 --> 00:01:38,916
it will be utter doom.

26
00:01:39,292 --> 00:01:42,207
Xiao Yan, do you dare to accept?

27
00:01:45,792 --> 00:01:47,041
Bring it on!

28
00:01:48,042 --> 00:01:51,166
It is time to settle the grudges of these years.

29
00:01:56,833 --> 00:01:59,791
What are the rules of this challenge?

30
00:02:01,792 --> 00:02:03,166
Best of three.

31
00:02:03,292 --> 00:02:04,666
Three fighters each.

32
00:02:04,667 --> 00:02:06,374
A fight to the death.

33
00:02:06,833 --> 00:02:07,833
Of course...

34
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:11,124
if you wish for a full-scale war, this Hall Master won't object.

35
00:02:11,667 --> 00:02:14,249
The Soul Hall has stood in Central Plains for so many years...

36
00:02:14,583 --> 00:02:19,166
it is not something you can resist just by cobbling together some alliances.

37
00:02:21,375 --> 00:02:23,082
If we truly engage in an all-out war...

38
00:02:23,208 --> 00:02:25,791
even if the Tianfu Alliance is annihilated...

39
00:02:26,042 --> 00:02:29,207
your Soul Hall will be crippled by eighty or ninety percent.

40
00:02:30,333 --> 00:02:33,957
Seems the Soul Clan is reluctant to bear such losses.

41
00:02:38,083 --> 00:02:41,374
Choose between the two options.

42
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,166
Best of three...

43
00:02:43,583 --> 00:02:46,207
accommodating your wish is a fine virtue.

44
00:02:46,875 --> 00:02:48,749
Send forth your combatants.

45
00:02:51,458 --> 00:02:52,707
These years...

46
00:02:53,083 --> 00:02:56,916
the greatest challenge my Soul Clan has faced is this.

47
00:02:57,583 --> 00:02:58,957
Xiao Clan whelp...

48
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:02,916
count me as one of your three.

49
00:03:19,583 --> 00:03:20,624
Xiao Chen.

50
00:03:24,125 --> 00:03:27,457
The Soul Clan's dogs are still skulking in the shadows.

51
00:03:31,958 --> 00:03:34,291
Worthy of the Bloody Axe Xiao Chen.

52
00:03:36,542 --> 00:03:40,166
Even after all these years, you remain this barbaric.

53
00:03:41,625 --> 00:03:42,749
Hun Qian Mo...

54
00:03:44,542 --> 00:03:47,666
you trash who begged for mercy before our Clan Chief...

55
00:03:48,042 --> 00:03:49,457
still have the face to show yourself?

56
00:03:51,958 --> 00:03:55,832
No matter how formidable he was, he ultimately fell.

57
00:03:56,042 --> 00:03:58,707
The victor is king.

58
00:03:59,083 --> 00:04:00,749
The current Soul Clan...

59
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,832
still stands atop this continent.

60
00:04:03,958 --> 00:04:05,749
And what of Xiao Xuan?

61
00:04:07,708 --> 00:04:08,749
The name of the Clan Chief...

62
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,749
is not for ants like you to utter.

63
00:04:20,458 --> 00:04:21,458
Xiao Chen...

64
00:04:21,708 --> 00:04:24,332
even if you survived luckily until now...

65
00:04:24,375 --> 00:04:25,874
the current you...

66
00:04:25,958 --> 00:04:28,166
is no match for the Bloody Axe Xiao Chen of old.

67
00:04:33,417 --> 00:04:37,207
The current you is no match for this old man.

68
00:04:42,958 --> 00:04:44,666
The aura of Xiao Xuan...

69
00:04:47,042 --> 00:04:50,582
let this old man serve as the vanguard.

70
00:04:55,625 --> 00:04:56,625
Xiao Yan.

71
00:04:56,958 --> 00:04:58,916
My three warriors are ready.

72
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,624
It is your turn.

73
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:03,791
Hun Qian Mo's strength is around 6-star...

74
00:05:04,167 --> 00:05:05,666
none of us can contend with him.

75
00:05:07,417 --> 00:05:08,957
Six-star Dou Sheng...

76
00:05:15,042 --> 00:05:16,207
Such a lively gathering...

77
00:05:16,375 --> 00:05:18,124
how could this old ancestor be missing?

78
00:05:24,417 --> 00:05:25,417
What is that?

79
00:05:25,441 --> 00:05:44,741
(Watch the Latest Donoghue Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

80
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,291
So many people...

81
00:05:47,625 --> 00:05:48,625
Old Ancestor...

82
00:05:49,542 --> 00:05:50,332
Greetings, Senior.

83
00:05:50,333 --> 00:05:51,333
Enough.

84
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:55,749
Old ghost of the Dan Tower...

85
00:05:57,292 --> 00:05:59,874
leave this old immortal to me.

86
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
Old ghost...

87
00:06:02,208 --> 00:06:04,707
in the past, for your sake...

88
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,957
my Soul Clan did not move against the Dan Tower.

89
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,249
For you to do this now...

90
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,707
is unwise.

91
00:06:10,917 --> 00:06:13,874
Now, the Dan Tower is a member of the Tianfu Alliance.

92
00:06:14,042 --> 00:06:15,541
Shared glory...

93
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:16,542
shared loss.

94
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:18,999
As a Guardian of the Dan Tower...

95
00:06:19,542 --> 00:06:22,916
this old ancestor naturally cannot stay out of it.

96
00:06:24,375 --> 00:06:25,666
It seems you are determined...

97
00:06:25,667 --> 00:06:27,916
to oppose my Soul Clan to the bitter end.

98
00:06:28,417 --> 00:06:29,666
Less talk, more action.

99
00:06:30,083 --> 00:06:31,083
Take this!

100
00:06:40,667 --> 00:06:41,667
Old ghost...

101
00:06:41,708 --> 00:06:43,166
the space outside is too cramped.

102
00:06:43,333 --> 00:06:44,457
Dare to enter?

103
00:06:45,208 --> 00:06:46,374
Why would I fear you?

104
00:06:50,042 --> 00:06:52,791
Worthy of an old ghost who survived in the Soul Clan for so long.

105
00:06:52,917 --> 00:06:54,249
You still have some guts.

106
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:57,750
Old thing...

107
00:06:58,042 --> 00:07:00,957
you have sabotaged my Soul Clan's plans time and again.

108
00:07:01,458 --> 00:07:03,624
Today, I will finish you off!

109
00:07:24,083 --> 00:07:25,083
Explode!

110
00:07:29,125 --> 00:07:30,125
Old Ancestor...

111
00:07:30,875 --> 00:07:34,124
to think you could fight Elder Qian Mo to a standstill.

112
00:07:34,542 --> 00:07:36,166
With this old ghost interfering...

113
00:07:36,542 --> 00:07:38,957
Hall Master, this might end in a loss for us.

114
00:07:39,542 --> 00:07:41,999
Mo'er, just watch the others for me.

115
00:07:42,167 --> 00:07:43,624
Leave Xiao Yan to me.

116
00:07:43,833 --> 00:07:45,291
I know what I am doing.

117
00:07:56,042 --> 00:07:57,416
Hungry for so long...

118
00:07:57,542 --> 00:07:59,457
it is time to come out and eat.

119
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,250
Retreat quickly!

120
00:08:58,250 --> 00:08:59,250
Senior...

121
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:15,500
Old ghost...

122
00:09:15,708 --> 00:09:19,166
save your breath and prepare your final words.

123
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:24,041
In these thousand years, your strength hasn't grown...

124
00:09:24,208 --> 00:09:26,582
but your lip service has improved greatly.

125
00:09:27,708 --> 00:09:29,207
Can't even stand steadily...

126
00:09:29,208 --> 00:09:30,707
still daring to talk tough?

127
00:09:31,875 --> 00:09:34,249
Senior, leave the rest to us.

128
00:09:34,417 --> 00:09:35,499
Please, go rest.

129
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,541
Very well, I leave it to you.

130
00:09:42,167 --> 00:09:43,167
Old Ancestor...

131
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:45,166
How should we judge this round?

132
00:09:48,625 --> 00:09:50,082
Don't be ungrateful.

133
00:09:50,333 --> 00:09:52,041
With this old thing interfering...

134
00:09:52,042 --> 00:09:54,582
achieving a draw is already quite good.

135
00:09:56,542 --> 00:09:57,749
Consider yourselves lucky.

136
00:09:58,125 --> 00:09:59,624
We'll call it a draw.

137
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,666
Hun Mo Old Ghost...

138
00:10:09,833 --> 00:10:11,041
get out here!

139
00:10:20,083 --> 00:10:21,541
Bloody Axe Xiao Chen...

140
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:24,957
I will deal with you, this outdated fellow.

141
00:10:28,083 --> 00:10:29,249
Outdated or not...

142
00:10:29,417 --> 00:10:30,957
we'll know after exchanging blows.

143
00:11:21,042 --> 00:11:22,666
Earth-Splitting Slash!

144
00:11:54,583 --> 00:11:56,082
Is this all you've got?

145
00:11:56,458 --> 00:12:00,332
You've completely disgraced the prestige Xiao Xuan earned.

146
00:12:03,667 --> 00:12:04,667
Shatter!

147
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:11,749
Sky Demon Blood Gu!

148
00:12:30,292 --> 00:12:31,292
Soul Gu Toad!

149
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:34,499
This Hun Mo Old Man's methods are truly vicious.

150
00:12:35,833 --> 00:12:36,833
Go!

151
00:13:01,042 --> 00:13:02,166
Die!

152
00:13:07,833 --> 00:13:10,916
Has it all ended?

153
00:13:11,208 --> 00:13:13,457
Xiao Chen, you can go rest...

154
00:13:14,083 --> 00:13:16,374
I will handle the Xiao Clan's affairs.

155
00:13:17,292 --> 00:13:18,292
Big brother...

156
00:13:18,792 --> 00:13:22,041
didn't you say that possessing strength allows one to protect everything?

157
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:24,541
I have been chasing after you...

158
00:13:25,042 --> 00:13:27,166
wanting to stand tall and upright just like you.

159
00:13:27,833 --> 00:13:29,457
Who knew fate would play tricks...

160
00:13:30,042 --> 00:13:32,291
leaving me stubborn and alone.

161
00:13:40,542 --> 00:13:41,542
Ancestor...

162
00:13:44,917 --> 00:13:46,874
if this is Heaven's trial...

163
00:13:47,292 --> 00:13:49,082
given to the Xiao Clan...

164
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:51,541
then let me pay any price...

165
00:13:52,292 --> 00:13:53,957
to guard the Xiao Clan.

166
00:14:24,292 --> 00:14:25,957
Late Five-star Dou Sheng.

167
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,332
Heaven-Cleaving Slash!

168
00:15:19,625 --> 00:15:21,832
Slash the Heavens!

169
00:16:10,125 --> 00:16:10,957
Ancestor...

170
00:16:11,125 --> 00:16:11,957
are you alright?

171
00:16:15,042 --> 00:16:16,042
I am fine.

172
00:16:16,458 --> 00:16:17,749
Another draw.

173
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:18,916
Next...

174
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,332
we can only rely on you.

175
00:16:30,208 --> 00:16:31,749
Another draw...

176
00:16:31,875 --> 00:16:35,041
Elder Hun Mo really overestimated himself this time.

177
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,582
This old man said long ago...

178
00:16:37,708 --> 00:16:39,916
that a direct full-scale war would be simpler.

179
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:42,666
Now, you are stuck in a dilemma.

180
00:16:43,583 --> 00:16:45,416
If you truly lose...

181
00:16:45,792 --> 00:16:48,166
let's see how you explain it to the Clan.

182
00:16:48,792 --> 00:16:51,416
The Soul Hall is a crucial part of the Clan's plan...

183
00:16:51,667 --> 00:16:54,082
it should not be used to clash head-on like this.

184
00:16:55,708 --> 00:16:57,124
Hurry and prepare.

185
00:16:57,417 --> 00:16:59,082
That brat is very cunning...

186
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,957
and now he possesses the Pure Lotus Demon Flame.

187
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:04,791
Do not capsize in the gutter.

188
00:17:05,083 --> 00:17:06,749
Pure Lotus Demon Flame...

189
00:17:07,917 --> 00:17:10,041
this Hall Master is quite curious to see it.

190
00:17:10,458 --> 00:17:12,499
In his hands...

191
00:17:12,958 --> 00:17:14,916
how much power can it display?

192
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:33,440
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

